        <abstract>
            <p>Praises CL’s work on human species.</p> 
<p>A critical review of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> in <hi rend="italic">Saturday Review</hi> [24 Dec 1859].</p> 
            <p>A letter from J. G. Jeffreys criticises CD’s geological statements.</p> 
<p>A note from William Whewell concerning <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
